Scene open
    Start()
        First level load
        End of first level load --> GameStart()
    GameStart() // Can Play Now
        OnGameStart.Invoke
            Player can move
            ui manager fades in HUD
LevelCompleted()
    Next Level Load
    Fade out HUD
    Lock Player Controls
    End of next level load --> GameStart()
PlayerDied()
    Same Level Load
    Lock Player Controls
    End of level load --> GameStart()
PauseGame()
    Pause Game Event
    Change UI
ResumeGame()
    Resume Game Event
    Change UI